## Code rules (CRITICAL)
- No comments in code
- No relative imports — use `@modules/`, `@constants/` aliases only
- All functions must have explicit return types
- No `console.log` — use NestJS Logger

## After implementing
Run type-check:
```bash
cd /Users/4thwithme/Documents/repo/no-name-proj/backend && npm run type-check
```
Fix any errors. Then commit:
```bash
git add src/constants/db.constant.ts src/modules/github/types/
git commit -m "feat: add db constants and interfaces for github data ingestion tables"
```

